* Within 3 months after the approval of the NEEAP, the Ministry shall submit to the Energy Community Secretariat (the 'Secretariat') a report prepared in accordance with Article 5(3) of this Law on alternative policy measures, which shall include information on achieving the required amount of energy savings through alternative policy measures and meeting the criteria of alternative policy measures provided for by the same article.
